	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Horizontal mirroring for horizontal scrolling allows raster effects such as raising the weapon menu out of the floor, or a rising and falling ceiling or floor. See also the first fortress in SMB3.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


